25|$|In November 2011, Oregon Governor John Kitzhaber {{announced}} {{a moratorium on}} executions in Oregon, canceling a planned execution and ordering a review of <b>the</b> <b>death</b> <b>penalty</b> system <b>in</b> <b>the</b> state.|$|R
